summary:
🐺 Arya Stark appreciation 20/- 

  But it was Jon Snow she thought of most. She wished somehow they could come to the Wall...
caption:
🐺 Arya Stark appreciation 20/-

But it was Jon Snow she thought of most. She wished somehow they could come to the Wall before Winterfell, so Jon might muss up her hair and call her “little sister.” She’d tell him, “I missed you,” and he’d say it too at the very same moment, the way they always used to say things together. She would have liked that. 

She would have liked that better than anything.
